org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.list
Class AeCatalogItemDetail

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.list.AeCatalogItem
      org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.list.AeCatalogItemDetail
public class AeCatalogItemDetail
extends AeCatalogItem

Essentially a struct that wraps the detail information for a single catalog resource deployment. Information includes the location hint, the target namespace, the actual resource (e.g. wsdl) (as a string), and an array of AeCatalogItemPlanReference objects that represent the process plans that utilize this resource.
